    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1711562903\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PlanetBlight 是一款什么样的游戏？</h2>?PlanetBlight 是一款以生存为主题的第一人称生存游戏。<br><br>为了探索和生存，玩家必须收集资源、调查建筑和设施，并制作生存所需的设备。<br>危险无处不在，玩家必须建造据点或制作强大的武器和盔甲、<br>随着玩家等级的提高，可以使用获得的技能点数解锁枪支附件和技能，让他们在战斗中射击更加精准可靠。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.poster.avif?t=1711562903\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.webm?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.mp4?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/884f96217ee6445e60dcdd6681896d35.poster.avif?t=1711562903\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/884f96217ee6445e60dcdd6681896d35.webm?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/